=item B<_story_link_as_item_with_edit>

 _story_link_as_item_with_edit topic story_id

Shows a link to a story, as an element of a list. If authorized,
shows also a link to edit it.
=cut
<li>
{-if|{-is_future_story|$0|$1}|<em>|}
	<a href='{-l|STORY|topic=$0|id=$1}'>{-story_title|$0|$1}</a>
{-if|{-is_future_story|$0|$1}|</em>|}
{-if|{-is_topic_editor|$0}|
	- <small><a href = '{-l|EDIT_STORY|topic=$0|id=$1}'>[Modificar]</a></small>
}
</li>
